{"tid":1091061,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[暗黑轉型］DC 電影轉合家歡","createTime":"2019-04-04T01:25:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T03:31:29.000Z","uid":167658,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6e776018db572dc2dc87d0a125d432d5ffcf223a","tid":1091061,"uid":167658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T01:25:41.000Z","msg":"荷李活近年掀起超級英雄熱潮，各大電影公司爭相發展自家電影宇宙。當中Marvel和DC兩巨頭經常被比較，Marvel近年接連交出多部賣座大片，DC作品包括《自殺特攻：超能暴隊》（Suicide Squad）、《正義聯盟》（Justice League）等卻票房、評價雙失，有指所屬電影公司華納兄弟高層決定今後放棄主攻成人市場的暗黑風格，改走合家歡溫馨路線。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《復仇者4》剛於北美地區開始預售，首日頭六個小時已打破電影史上預售票房紀錄成為冠軍，更撼贏《星球大戰：原力覺醒》（Star Wars：The Force Awakens）於2015年創下的紀錄。"},{"pid":"669d7388220e081901f89476741f24fd3716118c","tid":1091061,"uid":167658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T01:42:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d5ae8ad1c3fc5129eb87dede01b8d59bbf4e13","tid":1091061,"uid":194415,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T07:08:08.000Z","msg":"joker 都係合家歡？"},{"pid":"c78e9ff3f0be30bd975df8e70e4e716a74cbca1b","tid":1091061,"uid":119223,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T08:10:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>荷<del>李活近年掀起超級英雄熱潮，各大電影公司爭相發展自家電影宇宙。當中Marvel和DC兩巨頭經常被比較，Marvel近年接連交出多部賣座大片，DC作品包括《自殺特攻：超能暴隊》（Suicide Squad）、《正義聯盟》（Justice League）等卻票房、評價雙失，有指所屬電影公司華納兄弟高層決定今後放棄主攻成人市場的暗黑風格，改走合家歡溫馨路線。</del><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《復仇者4》剛於北美地區開始預售，首日頭六個小時已打破電影史上預售票房紀錄成為冠軍，更撼贏《星球大戰：原力覺醒》（Star Wars：The Force Awakens）於2015年創下的紀錄。</blockquote><br />\n今次票房破唔破到阿凡達? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebaf8dc6d2121366bc1c4c66abc631ce90864569","tid":1091061,"uid":60092,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T08:12:50.000Z","msg":"JL嗰陣，佢搵咗屎波子去做宣傳，我就知DC嘅目標觀眾係小學雞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d358823844dcd9a30bc380d916726a14f8a0277","tid":1091061,"uid":121546,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:40:20.000Z","msg":"係咪得香港既marvel同dc fans咁鐘意對罵?佢地唔睇其他超級英雄電影?<br />\n得香港d youtuber介紹電影要澄清自己冇收到dc同marvel錢,香港人真係痴撚線"},{"pid":"5fee94e1a110ab63ef380315488d7f8019ff6ee5","tid":1091061,"uid":159183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:17:32.000Z","msg":"睇導演風格既姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bedc3cdb1787bfd72dc453f6431e6ba7ff6064b","tid":1091061,"uid":159183,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MOFKJAz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMOFKJAz.png&h=134bfe3c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f1775bd94cdc30ae89a2942a87f3ce615eff620","tid":1091061,"uid":18265,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:20:53.000Z","msg":"啱啱咪出咗joker trailer"},{"pid":"29a5d31c5f30f512dddf8edec4070197566950d7","tid":1091061,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:21:41.000Z","msg":"轉左dc班高層先得唔得?"},{"pid":"b8931a00941887617ac0092e122841dc5947c3aa","tid":1091061,"uid":152432,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T14:14:17.000Z","msg":"Joker套戲都未上d人就開始打飛機"},{"pid":"13f959907317f71d01f171b0b9993018b75c6c34","tid":1091061,"uid":159183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8931a00941887617ac0092e122841dc5947c3aa","tid":1091061,"uid":152432,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"reply