me":"2019-04-07T18:08:19.000Z","msg":"DC預告一向好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb708ca67d0ea1fcca0ea167016e166ecd734bb","tid":1091061,"uid":135867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T18:13:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RZTz7su.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRZTz7su.jpg&h=244f781e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8dc79e55d1244cd53aceffa9e43deeadc7b35d91","tid":1091061,"uid":3549,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ebaf8dc6d2121366bc1c4c66abc631ce90864569","tid":1091061,"uid":60092,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T08:12:50.000Z","msg":"JL嗰陣，佢搵咗屎波子去做宣傳，我就知DC嘅目標觀眾係小學雞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T18:15:07.000Z","msg":"諗起就想笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n神奇女俠：Whats your name?<br />\n波子哥哥：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>smiling boris</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b736a2efd62e3b89026acfbd62b9863b5eea8c19","tid":1091061,"uid":75050,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T18:39:56.000Z","msg":"DC fans 一到店，所有喝酒的人便都看着他笑，有的叫道，「DC fans，DCEU腰斬了！」他不回答，對櫃裏說，「要一盒《Justice League》 Director's Cut 藍光DVD。」便排出九文大錢。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「《正義聯盟》正一垃圾！」DC fans 睜大眼睛說，「你怎麼這樣憑空汚人清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前年親眼見《正義聯盟》票房仆直，被《雷神3》吊着打。」DC fans便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「公映版不能算DC&hellip;&hellip;電影！&hellip;&hellip;沒有導演剪接版，能算DC電影麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「路蘭Batman三部曲」，什麼「Watchmen得過雨果獎」之類，引得衆人都鬨笑起來：店內外充滿了快活的空氣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b35bbbada6bc471eb9204d25bd9a8fff89ab19b","tid":1091061,"uid":167658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b736a2efd62e3b89026acfbd62b9863b5eea8c19","tid":1091061,"uid":75050,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T18:39:56.000Z","msg":"DC fans 一到店，所有喝酒的人便都看着他笑，有的叫道，「DC fans，DCEU腰斬了！」他不回答，對櫃裏說，「要一盒《Justice League》 Director's Cut 藍光DVD。」便排出九文大錢。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「《正義聯盟》正一垃圾！」DC fans 睜大眼睛說，「你怎麼這樣憑空汚人清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前年親眼見《正義聯盟》票房仆直，被《雷神3》吊着打。」DC fans便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「公映版不能算DC&hellip;&hellip;電影！&hellip;&hellip;沒有導演剪接版，能算DC電影麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「路蘭Batman三部曲」，什麼「Watchmen得過雨果獎」之類，引得衆人都鬨笑起來：店內外充滿了快活的空氣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:07:08.000Z","msg":"喺地鐵笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622bf589456c9ae377a1ad4deca6ee7dd3f9434b","tid":1091061,"uid":238296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29a5d31c5f30f512dddf8edec4070197566950d7","tid":1091061,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T13:21:41.000Z","msg":"轉左dc班高層先得唔得?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:09:35.000Z","msg":"華納班友先係最大問題"},{"pid":"c65589597e9380aee660d0d1ac1d0cf62329878a","tid":1091061,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b736a2efd62e3b89026acfbd62b9863b5eea8c19","tid":1091061,"uid":750